      "trigger": "coord_event_x24_y14_crystal_only",
      "description": "Suicune encounter scene. Only fires when SCENE_ROUTE42_SUICUNE is active (Crystal only, after seeing Suicune on Route 36). Suicune plays shock emote, slides away north-right off the map, then disappears. Sets SCENE_ROUTE42_NOOP and advances Suicune's roaming chain to Route 36 via SCENE_ROUTE36_SUICUNE. Also clears EVENT_SAW_SUICUNE_ON_ROUTE_36."
