  "notes": "Route 42 is a wide east-west route connecting Ecruteak City (via gate on west edge) to Mahogany Town. The northern cliff wall is Mt. Mortar, which has three cave entrances reachable from the route — western entrance near x=10, central at x=28, and eastern at x=46 (tile coords). The western third contains a pond that requires Surf to cross fully; the hidden Max Potion is in or adjacent to this pond. Three Apricorn trees (Pink, Green, Yellow) sit in the southeast corner. Trainer distribution: Fisher Tully is east-center (Pokegear rematch, Water Stone gift), Hiker Benjamin is far east (spinning), Pokemaniac Shane is far east near cave. Crystal adds the Suicune encounter scene. Map attribute tileset: $05 (outside). Connections: WEST | EAST."
